name: Plane crash into lighthouse
description: Arnheim 1.0 is described here https://www.chrisantha.co.uk/post/arnheim-1-0-overpainting-on-photographs and published here https://arxiv.org/abs/2105.00162 It produces a picture by evolving a neural visual grammar, fitness being defined by a duel encoder conditioned on the text string "Plane crash into lighthouse". These were my very first experiments in overpainting with it.
